flowchart TD
    REQ[User Request] --> TOOL[Agent generates tool call]
    TOOL --> CHECK{Requires approval?}
    CHECK -->|No| EXEC[Auto-execute]
    CHECK -->|Yes| INT[Interrupt triggered]
    INT --> DEC{Decision type}
    DEC -->|approve| RUN[Execute as-is]
    DEC -->|edit| EDIT[Edit then execute]
    DEC -->|reject| REJ[Reject + feedback]
    RUN --> RESUME[Resume execution]
    EDIT --> RESUME
    REJ --> RESUME
    EXEC --> RESUME
    RESUME --> RESULT[Return result]
